resources.string:
Please define intent-filter for com.kayac.nakamap.sdk.activity.NakamapActivity in AndroidManifest.xml as folling.

 <intent-filter>
 <action android:name="android.intent.action.VIEW" />
 <category android:name="android.intent.category.DEFAULT" />
 <category android:name="android.intent.category.BROWSABLE" />
 <data android:scheme="nakamapapp-%1$s" />
 </intent-filter>
App version of Nakamap\n\nEnjoy chat more conveniently!
